## Integration Test Threading

Integration tests hit a shared live Lemonade Server. When `LEMONADE_URL` is
set, all modules' integration tests run concurrently by default, causing
intermittent GPU/NPU resource contention on the server side.

**Always run the full test suite with `--test-threads=1`.** `dev.sh` sets this
flag automatically when it detects `LEMONADE_URL` in the environment.

```bash
cargo test --workspace -- --test-threads=1                         # always
LEMONADE_URL=http://localhost:13305/api/v1 ./dev.sh --backend-only # dev.sh handles it
```

