## Cross-cutting files worth knowing

- [ARCHITECTURE.md](mdc:ARCHITECTURE.md) — workspace layout, SQLite schema,
  inference design, design decisions. **Read this first** for any architectural
  work.
- [env.sh](mdc:env.sh) — optional. Sets `UFORGE_*` path variables only; no
  longer required for compilation.
- [dev.sh](mdc:dev.sh) — development runner. Auto-sets `--test-threads=1` when
  `LEMONADE_URL` is present.
- [defaults/schemas/](mdc:defaults/schemas/) — 13 TTRPG JSON schema files
  (workspace root, not inside any crate).
- [defaults/data/memory.jsonl](mdc:defaults/data/memory.jsonl) — Foundation
  universe sample data (~220 nodes, ~312 edges). Canonical JSONL format.

All per-file roles and types are covered by comments inside each source file.
Browse the crate source directly rather than duplicating a file index here.
